@startuml 31 Flavors
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ConditionEndStyle hline
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
start

repeat :**Read source class from project**;
    if (**Class is generated by the jOOQ code generator**\n----\nClass is preceded by comment "This class is generated by jOOQ.") then (yes)
        if (**Class represents a database table**\n----\nClass implements org.jooq.Table) then (yes)
            repeat :**Read next column definition in class**\n----\nNext class field of type TableField;
                if (**Column is of ENUM type**\n----\nDetermined by the second argument of\ncreateField (contains asEnumDataType)) then (yes)
                    :**Detect antipattern** (line span:\ncolumn definition);
                (no) elseif (**Column has a CHECK constraint**\n----\nDetermined from the getChecks method, looking\nfor constraints involving this column) then (yes)
                    if (**CHECK constraint's only purpose is to check the value against a list of values**\n(including ranges of discrete values with business meaning)\n----\n(((info_document_sex = 'M'::"char") OR (info_document_sex = 'F'::"char")))\n(((payment_method)::text = ANY ((ARRAY['BTC'::character varying, 'ETH'::character varying, ...)))\n(((order_status >= 0) AND (order_status <= 3)))\n----\n**But not:**\n((age > 0))\n(((name)::text <> ''::text))\n(((event_geo_lat >= ('-90'::integer)::double precision) AND (event_geo_lat <= (90)::double precision)))) then (yes)
                        :**Detect antipattern** (line span:\ncheck constraint definition);
                    endif
                endif
            repeat while (**Class has another column definition?**) is (yes) not (no)
        endif
    endif
repeat while (**Project contains another source class?**) is (yes) not (no)

stop
@enduml
